### Responsible Disclosure

If you discover vulnerabilities using techniques from this repository:
1. Follow responsible disclosure practices
2. Contact vendors through appropriate security channels
3. Allow reasonable time for patching (typically 90 days)
4. Do not exploit vulnerabilities in production systems

